purpose:
Defines the bounded architectural role of 019.interface.

required_behavior:
- route intent must be explicit
- actor boundary must be explicit
- screen and service relation must be explicit
- validation and failure behavior must be explicit

actor_boundary:
- viewer
- operator
- reviewer
- approver
- adapter

decision_matrix:
- read surface stays bounded
- action surface requires validated route
- masked outputs remain visibly masked
- ambiguity fails closed
